112
00:07:10,847 --> 00:07:11,847
Mr. Kunikida.

113
00:07:12,223 --> 00:07:13,544
We'll have
considerable difficulty

114
00:07:13,726 --> 00:07:15,526
if you can't come up
with some sort of answer.

115
00:07:16,227 --> 00:07:17,628
As you know, we
can't afford to make

116
00:07:17,730 --> 00:07:19,730
the very existence of the
aragami public knowledge,

117
00:07:20,566 --> 00:07:22,286
let alone that they
intend to destroy Japan.

118
00:07:23,817 --> 00:07:24,962
However, the government
intends to issue

119
00:07:24,986 --> 00:07:27,027
some kind of statement to
dispel the public concern.

120
00:07:28,282 --> 00:07:29,842
We've received inquiries
from all over the world

