reach epidemic proportions,

127
00:07:42,671 --> 00:07:44,791
and we must be prepared to
deal with it, Mr. Kunikida.

128
00:07:45,839 --> 00:07:46,675
Well, this is not the first time

129
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:48,640
that Japan has been faced
with such a problem.

130
00:07:49,303 --> 00:07:50,623
I would think our
state department

131
00:07:50,844 --> 00:07:52,164
would be rather
used to it by now.

132
00:07:52,889 --> 00:07:53,889
(chuckling)

133
00:07:55,849 --> 00:07:58,169
Well, first of all, we obviously
can't tell other countries

134
00:07:58,978 --> 00:08:00,618
that our nation kept
the aragami a secret.

135
00:08:01,690 --> 00:08:03,042
But if what you
tell me is correct,

136
00:08:03,066 --> 00:08:04,466
we'll have to come
up with something

137
00:08:04,735 --> 00:08:05,976
that at least sounds plausible.

138
00:08:06,110 --> 00:08:07,837
Maybe something to do
with mass hallucinations

139
00:08:07,861 --> 00:08:09,341
