175
00:09:40,955 --> 00:09:43,195
- [Sakura] Nuts, she just went
into the teachers' lounge.

176
00:09:43,957 --> 00:09:44,977
- [Kusanagi] I thought so.

177
00:09:45,001 --> 00:09:46,322
You're that
schizophrenic psychic.

178
00:09:47,086 --> 00:09:48,846
- [Sakura] Kusanagi,
what are you doing here?

179
00:09:50,674 --> 00:09:52,114
