185
00:10:12,153 --> 00:10:13,153
(clanging)

186
00:10:14,071 --> 00:10:14,573
Huh?

187
00:10:14,988 --> 00:10:15,364
Momiji?

188
00:10:15,949 --> 00:10:16,949
I'm sorry, excuse me.

189
00:10:19,993 --> 00:10:20,496
