things to discuss.

195
00:10:29,463 --> 00:10:30,623
Just what are you doing here?

196
00:10:31,004 --> 00:10:32,004
Hunting for aragami?

197
00:10:33,049 --> 00:10:33,550
Well.

198
00:10:33,800 --> 00:10:34,800
(laughing nervously)

199
00:10:36,803 --> 00:10:37,803
(crying)

200
00:10:38,012 --> 00:10:39,893
- [Momiji] Why did I have
to run away like that?

201
00:10:40,139 --> 00:10:42,260
So what if Kusanagi and
Sakura do have a relationship?

202
00:10:43,644 --> 00:10:44,684
I feel like such an idiot.

203
00:10:50,567 --> 00:10:52,127
I first ran into Reiko
about a week ago.

204
00:10:55,154 --> 00:10:56,154
- [Woman] Reiko!

205
00:10:56,322 --> 00:10:57,322
Reiko, what happened?

206
00:10:58,031 --> 00:11:00,191
Don't worry, there's nothing
physically wrong with her.

207
00:11:01,745 --> 00:11:03,185
However, it's my
professional opinion

208
00:11:03,539 --> 00:11:04,579
that she's been possessed.

209
00:11:05,832 --> 00:11:06,832
