210
00:11:07,834 --> 00:11:08,834
Oh, look at this!

211
00:11:09,293 --> 00:11:10,293
What does it mean?

212
00:11:12,046 --> 00:11:13,046
It can't be.

213
00:11:13,130 --> 00:11:14,450
You look like
you've got some idea

214
00:11:15,049 --> 00:11:16,068
of what might be behind this.

215
00:11:16,092 --> 00:11:17,652
I think you'd better
tell me everything.

216
00:11:19,052 --> 00:11:19,721
What, who are you?

217
00:11:19,888 --> 00:11:21,208
I'm the world's
greatest exorcist.

218
00:11:22,473 --> 00:11:23,473
My success rate is 100%.

219
00:11:24,475 --> 00:11:25,796
I'm from Kusamikado
Faith Healers,

220
00:11:26,645 --> 00:11:27,925
and boy, are you
guys ever lucky.

221
00:11:30,481 --> 00:11:31,962
So anyway, after a
little negotiating,

222
00:11:32,316 --> 00:11:34,237
I've set myself up to
watch Reiko 24 hours a day,

223
00:11:35,278 --> 00:11:37,439
and since I have to stay as
close to her as possible...

224
00:11:37,781 --> 00:11:39,781
So that's why you transferred
into Momiji's school.

225
00:11:40,951 --> 00:11:43,071
