aragami that possessed her?

226
00:11:43,704 --> 00:11:45,184
I think so, but there
are alternatives

227
00:11:45,371 --> 00:11:46,371
that I can't ignore.

228
00:11:47,874 --> 00:11:48,874
Alternatives?

